    Selected Features Proxy

    mlr_measures_selected_features_proxy.Rd

    Proxy measure that simply returns 0. Can be used as a proxy measure which is updated within an optimizer. Only to be used internally.

    Dictionary

    This Measure can be instantiated via the dictionary mlr_measures or with the associated sugar function msr():

    mlr_measures$get("selected_features_proxy")
msr("selected_features_proxy")
